name: 雅各布·安德鲁·菲格罗亚
name_full: 雅各布·安德鲁·菲格罗亚 Jacob Andrew Figueroa
introduction: Jacob Andrew Figueroa is known for 9-1-1 (2021), Sneaky Pete (2019) and Animal Kingdom (2016).He is also a writer/director known for The Marigolds Listen (2021), Ravioli Man (2021), and Papaya Whip (2017).Jacob was born in Huntsville, Texas but lived all around Texas as well as Oklahoma and Tennessee before spending his high school years in San Antonio, Texas.Puerto Rican descent.
